title: Pat Woodell, Actress on 'Petticoat Junction,' Dies at 71
text:

Pat Woodell , who played one of the three original Bradley sisters on the 1960s CBS sitcom Petticoat Junction , died Sept. 29 at her home in Fallbrook, Calif., after a two-decade battle with cancer, the Los Angeles Times reported . Start the conversation, or Read more at Hollywood Reporter.
